name: Byte22-assembly-emulator
body:
### Welcome to Byte22 Assembly Emulator.
A simple Assembly Emulator built with HTML5 and Angular.js

```
$ git clone git@github.com:philpoore/byte22-assembly-emulator.git a
$ cd a
$ open index.html
```
Examples in the "examples/" folder ^__^

### Authors and Contributors
Main Author: @philpoore
Feel free to message me with issues, bugs and feature requests.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Byte22 Assembly Emulator...? :(

Message @philpoore for support.
